    "description": "Kandra: The Moonwalker is a 3D platformer demo inspired by the great classics of Nintendo 64 and PlayStation like <strong>Spyro</strong> or Banjo Kazooie. In Kandra's universe the other Moonwalkers have disappeared and with them the magic has diseppeared. <strong>Kandra</strong>'s goal as one of the <strong>last remaining Moonwalkers</strong> is to find her friends and recover the magic feathers.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Find collectibles!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829200/extras/51abc922f1dd9851f48eacd4316e3c10.poster.avif?t=1652778421\" width=620 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829200/extras/51abc922f1dd9851f48eacd4316e3c10.webm?t=1652778421\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829200/extras/51abc922f1dd9851f48eacd4316e3c10.mp4?t=1652778421\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Collect <strong>feathers</strong>, <strong>gems</strong> and other <strong>collectibles</strong> to unlock abilities, open portals and progress towards your goal: collecting all the magic feathers and returning magic to the world.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Defeat enemies and bosses!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829200/extras/52704df562959052df90589d3c1ae004.poster.avif?t=1652778421\" width=620 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829200/extras/52704df562959052df90589d3c1ae004.webm?t=1652778421\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829200/extras/52704df562959052df90589d3c1ae004.mp4?t=1652778421\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Fight against enemies that want to block your waym, from mere minions to <strong>bosses</strong>. Use different skills for different combat situations.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Get new skills for Kandra!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829200/extras/fbfc888b77b1f3de7ffed9810f672dfa.poster.avif?t=1652778421\" width=620 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829200/extras/fbfc888b77b1f3de7ffed9810f672dfa.webm?t=1652778421\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829200/extras/fbfc888b77b1f3de7ffed9810f672dfa.mp4?t=1652778421\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Unlock new <strong>skills</strong> to face enemies in new ways and overcome <strong>environmental challenges</strong>.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore the different worlds and bring back the magic!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829200/extras/ec0255bb1b75a9858ac03558682ed7ad.poster.avif?t=1652778421\" width=620 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829200/extras/ec0255bb1b75a9858ac03558682ed7ad.webm?t=1652778421\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829200/extras/ec0255bb1b75a9858ac03558682ed7ad.mp4?t=1652778421\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Explore worlds, help their <strong>inhabitants</strong>, beat the bad guys and collect <strong>gems</strong> and <strong>feathers</strong> to restore order.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Do you want to learn to create videogames like Kandra the Moonwalker?</h2>Use our link to access our free course and create your first 3D game in Unity today ",
